Key Interview Points

VNet = Private network in Azure
Subnet = Division of VNet
NSG = Traffic filtering
VNet Peering = Connect VNets
VPN Gateway = Azure ⇄ On-Prem via Internet
ExpressRoute = Private dedicated connection
Private Endpoint = Private access to Azure services
Route Table = Controls packet routing


One-Line Interview Answer
Azure VNet is a logically isolated private network in Azure that enables secure communication between Azure resources, on-premises environments, and the internet
